711065f-a.title: Manhattan: 11th Street (East) - Avenue C
711065f-a.text:
East 11th Street, north side, east from but not including Ave. C, and showing tanks of the Consolidated Gas Company near the East River.
February 24, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.

717955f-a.title: Manhattan: Avenue C - 11th Street (East)
717955f-a.text:
Ave. C, north from East 11th Street. The house under demolition (seen on the left) is No. 187, between East 11th and East 12th Streets.
February 24, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
